{"word":"Example","slug":"example","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Example</b> - <b>(1) Christ's Example</b> to be followed<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=11&verse=29'>Mat 11:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=16&verse=24'>Mat 16:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=13&verse=15'>Joh 13:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=15&verse=5'>Rom 15:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=10&verse=1'>2Co 10:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=2&verse=5'>Phi 2:5</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=3&verse=13'>Col 3:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=3&verse=1'>Heb 3:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=12&verse=2'>Heb 12:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=2&verse=21'>1Pe 2:21</a><p/><b>(2) Evil Example</b> to be shunned<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=20&verse=23'>Lev 20:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=18&verse=9'>Deu 18:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=22&verse=24'>Pro 22:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=22&verse=25'>Pro 22:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=20&verse=18'>Eze 20:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=4&verse=11'>Heb 4:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=12&verse=15'>Heb 12:15</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=3&verse=17'>2Pe 3:17</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Evil Associations, ASSOCIATION<p/> ASSOCIATION<p/>Sinful Imitation, WORLDLINESS<p/><b>(3) Good Example,</b> General References to<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=13&verse=15'>Joh 13:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bible